OL,3,CWelsh leaders begin last full day of
OL,4,Ccampaigning ahead of pivotal election
OL,6,FWelsh political leaders have begun
OL,7,Ftheir final full day of campaigning
OL,8,Fahead of what is being described as a
OL,9,Fhistoric election.
OL,11,FAccording to the latest ITV Cymru
OL,12,FWales opinion poll, Plaid Cymru has
OL,13,Fjumped ahead and is predicted to be
OL,14,Fthe largest party in the Senedd, with
OL,15,F33% of the vote - four percentage
OL,16,Fpoints ahead of Reform UK at 29%.
OL,18,FPlaid Cymru's leader Rhun ap Iorwerth
OL,19,Fand his campaign team are in Llandudno
OL,20,Ffor their final push to convince
OL,21,Fvoters before polling day.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
