OL,3,CWelsh leaders begin last full day of
OL,4,Ccampaigning ahead of pivotal election
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, he said: "Just
OL,7,Fin this one constituency, we have
OL,8,Fknocked on 18,000 doors, that's a
OL,9,Fpattern that replicated across the
OL,10,Fconstituencies with Conservative
OL,11,Factivists in every corner of Wales."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, First Minister Eluned
OL,14,FMorgan is in Pembrokeshire, with the
OL,15,FLedwood Mechanical Engineering estate
OL,16,Fas the location for her final day of
OL,17,Fcampaigning.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
