OL,3,CWelsh leaders begin last full day of
OL,4,Ccampaigning ahead of pivotal election
OL,6,FWelsh Liberal Democrat Leader Jane
OL,7,FDodds is in Builth Wells. The Welsh
OL,8,FLib Dems have held at 6% which, in
OL,9,Fthis scenario, would elect Dodds in
OL,10,FBrycheiniog Tawe Nedd.
OL,12,FReform UK's Welsh leader Dan Thomas,
OL,13,Falong with Nigel Farage, held a large
OL,14,Fevent for voters in Merthyr Tydfil on
OL,15,FTuesday, 5 May.
OL,17,FNigel Farage said he will "run to the
OL,18,Fline, up until 10 o'clock Thursday."
OL,20,F"Let's be clear: we are fighting to
OL,21,Fcome first," he added.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
