OL,3,CWelsh leaders begin last full day of
OL,4,Ccampaigning ahead of pivotal election
OL,6,FDan Thomas said he is "confident, but
OL,7,Fnot complacent" that Reform UK can be
OL,8,Fthe biggest party in Wales,
OL,9,Femphasising that they are "fighting
OL,10,Ffor every vote" over the next 48 hours.
